<note n="0251001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0251001">原語有 Kiti saddo，應如底本之 Kitti saddo。</note>
<note n="0252002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0252002">Chandāvā brāhmanā 其他寫本缺此，想是誤會之插入。</note>
<note n="0255003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0255003">原語 andha-veṇi 另一本為 paveṇi veṇi 是辮髮之義，今取列之義。</note>
